Metadata-Version: 2.0
Name: django-sky-redirects
Version: 0.8.1
Summary: Robust redirect app for django that supports domain redirects and regex patterns.
Home-page: http://github.com/concentricsky/django-sky-redirects/
Author: Concentric Sky
Author-email: django@concentricsky.com
License: Apache 2.0
Platform: UNKNOWN

Usage
=====

add 'sky_redirects' to INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py::

   INSTALLED_APPS = (
      'sky_redirects',
      ...

Add the sky_redirects middleware to the *beginning* of MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES in settings.py::

   MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES = [
      'sky_redirects.middleware.DomainRedirectMiddleware',
      'sky_redirects.middleware.RegexRedirectMiddleware',
      ...


Then run syncdb, and you are ready to go!

